  • public final class QualityFastaRecordBuilder
extends AbstractFastaRecordBuilder<PhredQuality,QualitySequence,QualityFastaRecord,QualityFastaRecordBuilder>
    QualityFastaRecordBuilder is a factory class that makes instances of QualityFastaRecords. Depending on the different parameters, the factory might choose to return different implementations.

    dkatzel

    • Constructor Detail

      • QualityFastaRecordBuilder

        public QualityFastaRecordBuilder(String id,
                                 String entireRecordBody)
        Create a new builder instance for the given id and entire quality values as a human readable string.
        Parameters:
        id - the id of the quality fasta record; can not be null.
        entireRecordBody - a string representation of the quality sequence, must contain whitespace to separate quality values; each quality value may have leading zeros but can not be null.
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if either parameter is null.
